Valley Rolling Mills, Inc., Plaintiff, v. Irving J. Feldman, Trading under the Name of Columbia Tool & Supply Company, Appellant, and Charles T. Baird, Respondent, Impleaded with Another.

Reported below, 264 App. Div. 717.

Submitted July 29, 1942; decided October 8, 1942. *634Carl K. Harten for motion. Leo Sandler opposed.

Motion dismissed, with ten dollars costs and necessary printing disbursements on the ground that the application was not made within the time fixed by the Civil Practice Act.
